# DESCRIPTION
# Determine the domain and range of f(x) = B/x-A
#
# ENDDESCRIPTION
## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Functions)
## DBsection(Domain and range)
## Institution(John Wiley & Sons)
## Level(2)
## MO(1)
## MLT(algebra_functions_domain_range_a_over_bx_plus_c)

## TitleText1('Calculus')
## AuthorText1('Anton')
## EditionText1('9')
